    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. It retains its crisp throttle response and high-revving character. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides positive engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, and the Vanos system has been addressed to ensure variable valve timing precision. A true driver\u2019s machine with excellent mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
