    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2018 Executive Touring Sedan in Metallic Carbon Grey. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a buyer seeking luxury and reliability without the showroom price tag. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the turbocharged engine pulls cleanly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and it has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule\u2014I have the full service logs ready for your inspection. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though in the interest of full disclosure, there are minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the lower edge of the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment. The heated leather seats show light, natural creasing on the driver's bolster but remain soft and free of tears. All technology features, including the 12-speaker premium audio system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. The vehicle sits on alloy wheels with plenty of life left in the all-season tires. This is a complete, turn-key package for anyone looking for a dependable, high-end driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
