    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies engineering excellence and enduring value. This specimen has been curated to meet rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. Featuring a comprehensive service history and a refined profile, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering, which stands as a testament to diligent preservation and superior performance.",
      "price": 34900.0,
