    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a reliable vehicle without the massive price tag of a brand-new one. It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it for your daily commutes or weekend road trips! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see if it's the right fit for you. Feel free to shoot me any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
