    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded bushings to maintain structural integrity under lateral load. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. Though it exhibits minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil analysis and compression\u2014are excellent, ensuring this remains a high-performance driving tool.",
